---
description: LTS runtimes; maintained libs; pin majors where it matters
alwaysApply: true
---

# Stable stacks

- Prefer **LTS** runtimes; no EOL or pre-release in production mainlines.
- Pin majors where it matters (`engines`, `.nvmrc`, images, `go.mod`, etc.); CI matches dev.
- Libraries: maintained majors; avoid stale deps (~12mo no release, archived, critical CVEs).
- No alphas/betas on main—branch or flag instead.
- Upgrade before EOL; read changelogs; patch security promptly.
